## Schema 设计

```graphql
type Query {
  user(id: ID!): User
  users(filter: UserFilter, pagination: Pagination): UserConnection!
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  name: String!
  email: String!
  posts(first: Int = 10): PostConnection!
  avatar(size: ImageSize = MEDIUM): String
